aboutThisMasterclass: Are you hungry for some knowledge about the high-level design of food delivery apps? Look no further!

In this webinar, we'll delve into the delicious details of how apps like Swiggy and Zomato manage to bring your favourite meals straight to your door. From coordinating complex delivery logistics to satisfying your cravings in a snap, we'll explore the technology that made these apps highly successful.
topicsCoveredMasterclass: Understand the design & functionality of a food delivery app
Study the use of data flow diagrams for an online food ordering system
Familiarize yourself with real-time database management systems & NoSQL
Learn techniques for scaling a system to accommodate millions of users
